{"tid":845403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【限薪令惹的禍】傳電視台追回酬金差價 趙薇舒淇被勒令退4,563萬","createTime":"2018-10-02T15:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T09:11:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"ddcd1a9201a0a84b55889fd993089cb84b71df90","tid":845403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181002/58748036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F58748036&d=RqU6pVPmSc1SWWoYufi87TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9e69721e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F58748036&h=7b2760e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181002/58748036</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年10月02日 <br />\n<br />\n【限薪令惹的禍】傳電視台追回酬金差價 趙薇舒淇被勒令退4,563萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538473716_b669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538473716_b669.jpg&h=69899b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳湖南衛視向節目製作組追番趙薇（左）等人嘅酬金差價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n范冰冰涉稅務事件後，北京當局加大力度追明星稅，過去明星拿來避稅嘅影視公司、工作室陸續傳出倒閉或結業，令大陸影視圈嘅寒冬及早來到。之前廣電總局講過綜藝節目酬金要限制，做一集總酬金不超過80萬人民幣（約91.2萬港元），做一季度嘅明星總片酬不得超過1,000萬人民幣（約1,140.8萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n聽講有啲節目雖然係今年5、6月已簽約，一早俾晒錢，但節目因為o依家仲播緊出街，所以電視台有權向明星追番差價。<br />\n<br />\n聽聞趙薇、舒淇同蘇有朋等演出嘅《中餐廳》就被製作方追差價，當初趙薇同舒淇每人拍一季大約攞咗5,000萬人民幣（約5,704萬港元）酬勞，有傳佢哋要攞番4,000萬人民幣（約4,563萬港元）差價俾湖南衛視，電視台係將個節目批咗俾一間製作公司做，所以演員合約都係由社作公司簽，所以都係製作方去幫電視台追，知情者爆料話：「趙薇好明白國家政策，所以要追討差價就好聽話把錢退回來，但舒淇方面初時好像不太願意，後來要趙薇再打電話勸說，才答應退回來。」<br />\n<br />\n頭先打俾舒淇經理人管小姐，想問佢有冇咁嘅事，但佢一直冇回應。<br />\n王菲幫芒果衛視做嘅《幻樂之城》，聽聞一季就攞1億人仔，如果要吐番差價，即係成9000萬，真係好想知道王菲會唔會肯，畢竟當初都因為價高先吸引到佢做呢個節目。<br />\n<br />\n精選娛聞，喺晒《娛果》<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyent&d=RqU6pVPmSc1SWWoYufi87TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=58d789d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyent</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538473715_f4a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538473715_f4a9.jpg&h=765c78ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有指舒淇（左）起初唔係好想退錢，後來都有跟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538473715_05a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538473715_05a4.jpg&h=92901142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n節目中仲有蘇有朋演出<br />\n<br />\n 上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【甜到漏】老公陳豪出埠工作 陳茵媺貼相留言︰miss you<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【短片】【曾與韓君婷傳斷背情】經理人陳早茵貼身照顧 43歲佘詩曼話......"},{"pid":"63d8d2d9bc47afd3b104eefc720ecaecebb43142","tid":845403,"uid":13303,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 厲害了同香港一樣回收返人工"},{"pid":"f5acdc29f6e066858406ce7352aad3c4de9b557e","tid":845403,"uid":26752,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"幾時到香港班偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263ff7a8ae7b8f6097da6c1d7c338e1d2a6bb2c5","tid":845403,"uid":132587,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"大陸班藝人根本唔值<br />\n成個娛樂同影視圈水份都極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fcd261dc9e8daac5bc61f60cb45853dca7e2a1","tid":845403,"uid":7206,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"做啲戇鳩嘢又收幾千萬，唔怪得香港二、三線上到去都做「老師」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"